Transat A.T. Logo Transat A.T. Inc. is an international, vertically integrated tour operator with nearly 20 business units in 8 countries. The company is headquartered in Montreal, Quebec, Canada. In May 2021, Jean-Marc Eustache, then CEO and one of the principal founders of the company, announced he would retire, with Annick Guerard becoming president and CEO effective May 27, 2021. Source
